content: Hello Sri! Nice to meet you. I'm Master, the hiring officer for this position. Thank you for coming in for the technical round today. I hope you're prepared to discuss your skills and experience in more detail. Can you start by telling me a bit about your current project or a project you've worked on that you're particularly proud of?

So, you've worked on a project related to AI, specifically Complan. Can you elaborate on what Complan is and what your role was in the project? For example, what was the goal of the project, and what skills did you use to achieve it?
